Title: The renormalized $\phi^4_4$-trajectory by perturbation theory in the

running couplingAuthors: Christian Wieczerkowski (University of Muenster)

Comments: 23 pages LaTeX, Large momentum bound corrected

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B488 (1997) 441-465

We compute the renormalized trajectory of $\phi^4_4$-theory by perturbationtheory in a running coupling. We introduce an iterative scheme withoutreference to a bare action. The expansion is proved to be finite to every orderof perturbation theory.